326
00:27:43,620 --> 00:27:44,540
Penanggung jawab suasana.

327
00:27:44,980 --> 00:27:45,580
Makan satu.

328
00:27:47,180 --> 00:27:47,980
Xiaoxiao.

329
00:27:49,340 --> 00:27:51,500
