355
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:41,020
[Kalau begitu, aku akan jelaskan dulu peraturan permainan ini.]

356
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:42,380
Misalnya,

357
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:45,260
Keponakan menanyakan satu pertanyaan padaku

358
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:46,580
